# Maximum Length of Repeated Subarray

## Description

[doc](https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-length-of-repeated-subarray/)

## Solutions

### First Idea

```javascript
/**
 * @param {number[]} nums1
 * @param {number[]} nums2
 * @return {number}
 */
var findLength = function (nums1, nums2) {
  let max = 0

  for (let i = 0; i < nums1.length; i++) {
    const cur = nums1[i]

    for (let j = 0; j < nums2.length; j++) {
      const other = nums2[j]

      if (other === cur) {
        let k = 1
        while (k + i < nums1.length && k + j < nums2.length) {
          if (nums1[i + k] !== nums2[j + k]) {
            break
          }
          k++
        }
        max = Math.max(max, k)
      }
    }
  }

  return max
}
```

- Time Complexity: O(n^3)
- Space Complexity: O(1)

